{"tid":472014,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論][有感] 啱啱睇完戀愛與謊言，點解會無人討論？","createTime":"2017-11-17T19:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T14:28:08.000Z","uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"63b49ab43bd9a75e5d9cbbfe1a8a2b81fe97860d","tid":472014,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T19:50:27.000Z","msg":"套野真係好好睇 <br />\n無論作畫定bgm都好正<br />\n好耐都冇睇過咁胃痛同高質嘅動畫了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返劇情方面<br />\n一開始我覺得男主同美咲一齊係最好<br />\n完全可以放底莉莉奈<br />\n但可惜隨住劇情發展<br />\n男主同莉莉奈相處耐左，關係又好左<br />\n另外莉莉奈嘅性情亦開始有轉變<br />\n我就覺得開始胃痛啦<br />\n因為兩位嘅地位都開始平等<br />\n但女主始終得一個，一定要作出取捨<br />\n首先男主同美咲已經有好長好深嘅感情<br />\n互相都好愛大家<br />\n但同時莉莉奈同男主之間嘅感情又唔會輸比美咲<br />\n唔好話男主 我都唔知企邊邊好<br />\n<br />\n直到第十一二集<br />\n莉莉奈見到男主同美咲kiss係教堂個一幕<br />\n同埋同男住係房傾計同kiss個part<br />\n睇完之後我個心就好up住up住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔單止因為因為見到莉莉奈想忍痛離開<br />\n仲有因為果一kiss<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/024337_349381a597eb8d355f1ed8118d43c88c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F024337_349381a597eb8d355f1ed8118d43c88c.jpg&h=cc17d3f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全睇得出莉莉奈變到好唔捨得同開始愛上男主<br />\n依一part真係搞到我差啲流馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又胃痛又感動<br />\n<br />\n去到結局<br />\n見到兩位女主係換緍紗時嘅對話<br />\n我就好奇點解美咲話自己冇可能同男主一齊<br />\n亦選擇忍痛 只係背後守護同去愛男主<br />\n雖然唔明佢背負著咩原因<br />\n不惜用咁多謊言掩飾對男主嘅愛<br />\n但見佢每次都掩飾唔住<br />\n都睇得出佢真係好愛男住亦放唔底佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到動畫最後<br />\n雖然end得好勉強<br />\n但都算放底左心頭大石<br />\n起碼男主仲未有答案<br />\n<br />\n好想快啲睇下之後佢地發展成點<br />\n有冇ching可以話我知動畫去到漫畫第幾集<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我天日慢慢追<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比幾張圖大家回味下<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/11-17-2017/Y_1MkU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F11-17-2017%2FY_1MkU.gif&h=abeaa3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/11-17-2017/9xq6Yd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F11-17-2017%2F9xq6Yd.gif&h=58f197d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/11-17-2017/kHvOpJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F11-17-2017%2FkHvOpJ.gif&h=c4c7dca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申訓住打，有咩打錯記得屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"46e7118f87f710a846363e67b11e89fb8e5b3e7a","tid":472014,"uid":102208,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T19:51:27.000Z","msg":"順便搞個投票 睇下各位ching咩喜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美咲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/034255_eade5be691237396d24bd77283b2f04c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F034255_eade5be691237396d24bd77283b2f04c.jpg&h=adc95155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n莉莉奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/034307_67c52d768d3a617a8e7eb6ee8f676daa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F034307_67c52d768d3a617a8e7eb6ee8f676daa.jpg&h=a1127e42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d3d0613000b968419eff2efc77b87382f64a00a","tid":472014,"uid":87132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T19:57:35.000Z","msg":"可能我本身唔受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk